channel.title: Another building a PC thread
channel.description:
My PC needs upgrading. It predates the unreal tournament era. It was a beast back then, not so much now. I already got a case and 1TB HDD, so I wont have to buy those. I'm on a 800$ budget, with this build I'm over budget using components found on the web.
Intel Core i5 3570K CPU MSI Z77A-G45 MSI GeForce GTX 660 Ti Power Edition Corsair CX Series CX600M - 600 Watt Corsair Vengeance LP 1600-8GB (2x4GB)
